title: s'Teeblatt
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Organic, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery
description: A 100% vegan/vegetarian restaurant serves daily salads and soups. Also serves both vegan and vegetarian sweets. Freshly brewed teas available. Comfy atmosphere. Owner is also the chef. If you plan an event, you may ask for longer opening hours.
